                            <entry>
                    <title>GDCR 2014 Needs a Visual Designer!</title>
                    <link rel="alternate" href="http://coderetreat.org/xn/detail/6456126:BlogPost:37416"/>
                                        <id>tag:coderetreat.org,2014-07-31:6456126:BlogPost:37416</id>
                                        <updated>2014-07-31T02:30:00.000Z</updated>
                    
                                            <author>
                            <name>Jim Hurne</name>
                            <uri>http://coderetreat.org/profile/JimHurne</uri>
                        </author>
                    
                    <summary type="html">
                        &lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-size-3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UPDATE: Several volunteers have stepped up to help us with the website and the media pack. Thanks!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have ever &lt;a href=&quot;http://gdcr.coderetreat.org&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;visited the Global Day of Coderetreat event website&lt;/a&gt;, then you know how ugly it is. All our previous attempts to improve the site have not worked out. We ran a website design contest last year but we only received one entry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are…&lt;/p&gt;                    </summary>

                    <content type="html">
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;font-size-3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UPDATE: Several volunteers have stepped up to help us with the website and the media pack. Thanks!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have ever &lt;a href=&quot;http://gdcr.coderetreat.org&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;visited the Global Day of Coderetreat event website&lt;/a&gt;, then you know how ugly it is. All our previous attempts to improve the site have not worked out. We ran a website design contest last year but we only received one entry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are asking the community directly for help!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for &lt;strong&gt;volunteer visual designers&lt;/strong&gt; who have an interest in rebranding GDCR and changing our visual identity. We need help redesigning the Global Day of Coderetreat Website &lt;a href=&quot;http://globalday.coderetreat.org&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://globalday.coderetreat.org&lt;/a&gt;, logo, and media pack. The media pack typically includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Promotional Flyer Templates&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Sticker designs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Global Sponsor Prospectus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Local Sponsor Prospectus Template&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Email announcement templates&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Social Networks Page Design Template&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Talking points&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Press release templates&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Directional signs to the event (and bathrooms)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Style Guide&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We (the committee that organizes GDCR) are enthusiasts who use our personal time to organize the event. Additionally, we are not visual designers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is no budget for visual design. All funds received from sponsorships are used to promote, coordinate, and help fund community-based programming educational organizations (this year we supporting &lt;a href=&quot;http://coderdojo.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;CoderDojo&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a volunteer web developer and we are looking for at least one volunteer designer. We need your help!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in volunteering, the team would love to hear from you. Main guidelines will be provided, but your creativity and innovation are the only limits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested, please email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:gdcr@coderetreat.org&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;gdcr@coderetreat.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jim++&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
